com.dropbox.core.http

Class OkHttpRequestor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dropbox.core.http.HttpRequestor
      • com.dropbox.core.http.OkHttpRequestor

  • public class OkHttpRequestor
extends HttpRequestor
    HttpRequestor implementation that uses OkHttp. You can only use this if your project includes the OkHttp library.

    To use this, pass Instance to the DbxRequestConfig constructor.
